sec.p:
When forecasting the TB epidemiological patterns using the BSTS model, the mean absolute deviation (MAD), root-mean-square error (RMSE), mean absolute percentage error (MAPE), mean error rate (MER), and root-mean-square percentage error (RMSPE) were used to measure the predictive accuracy.
